{"tid":1969382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[相信政府唔戴]復活節長假郊遊　部分人脫下口罩遊玩","createTime":"2020-04-12T11:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T11:40:28.000Z","uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64e2a61f24413296df6d224065d9109b17b08093","tid":1969382,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:24:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=387525&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387525%26refer%3DShare&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=62210e7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387525%26refer%3DShare&h=29f6f26c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=387525&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】復活節長假無論市區抑或郊區都不難見到很多人，部分人亦放下警戒，脫下口罩遊玩，而在離島的食肆生意不錯，部分戶外座位，沒有按新規定分隔開。<br />\n<br />\n長假期又好天氣，大美督水壩彷彿回到疫情發生前，壩上很多單車和家庭式單車，非常熱鬧，小朋友追求速度感，大人就放慢腳步享受，部分人亦放下警戒不戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n誰人說風箏一定要放？學他這樣，一樣開心。<br />\n<br />\n若想與人拉遠一點距離，他們就選擇租小艇湖上泛舟，租艇的士多都忙過不停。<br />\n<br />\n碼頭旁的士多，有不少市民坐下吃東西，新規例下餐廳位置減少，有市民選擇租家庭單車在路旁用餐。<br />\n<br />\n很多人選擇去離島，結果由上船開始就多人，在長洲大街人頭湧湧。<br />\n<br />\n在長洲的食肆都相當好生意，茶餐廳等食肆都有按新規定，為顧客量體溫，但戶外座位餐枱沒有分隔1.5米，也沒有用膠板分開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FJBG2Ll.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFJBG2Ll.gif&h=3db317eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea8f8a33e1eaf9962365e5f8d06d1ad4bfa36ad9","tid":1969382,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/jZMKOz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FjZMKOz.gif&h=314b93c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25a6132adf8b5bb87283a693f47a4c19e516cb20","tid":1969382,"uid":20539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"中間自轉放風箏個巴打好有潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b27f6654ef80a5a170a3793cf3170d2ca70ce5e","tid":1969382,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"新乜撚冠人<br />\n<br />\n係就係武肺人。"},{"pid":"c9cdeb84ee36686dcd95410a92518d8dbc15d515","tid":1969382,"uid":20539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a6132adf8b5bb87283a693f47a4c19e516cb20","tid":1969382,"uid":20539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"中間自轉放風箏個巴打好有潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:29:02.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打cap出黎"},{"pid":"3c47ff1a0c8d2fe3051dce0e569a6d8a761cadeb","tid":1969382,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b27f6654ef80a5a170a3793cf3170d2ca70ce5e","tid":1969382,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"新乜撚冠人<br />\n<br />\n係就係武肺人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"好，夠30日我改呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a299491d98dea5396acc52b00692c51ab0d5b5f5","tid":1969382,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a6132adf8b5bb87283a693f47a4c19e516cb20","tid":1969382,"uid":20539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"中間自轉放風箏個巴打好有潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T11:40:28.000Z","msg":"柒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比新聞影曬binc都唔知"}]}